{
  "stem": "3097.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when I was ready to go, and the Ukrainian was sitting far away with the-- playing with his gun, with his rifle, Wasser run to me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, [INAUDIBLE], they caught Natka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]-- that was the policeman, a Jewish policeman, caught her, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She describes this in the book, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she describes that she went on the-- on the fence, and she got caught on the heel or something like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that isn't-- he caught her because she was not supposed to be there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was wearing a-- a-- it was May, and she was wearing a heavy coat, OK?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he said, what should we do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, we're going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I will not shoot anybody here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We have to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We have to sacrifice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Whatever will happen to us will happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we went, OK?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They caught her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took her to the Fuss, to this-- no, first to [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Spiegel, ?] to the chief of the police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He beat her up a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then he took her to Fuss.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fuss started to beat her, find out, where did we go?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My plans were to go to, maybe make contact with this-- with the Kosubec, who was a partisan.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But originally, I wanted to go maybe east, to more [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] areas which are more left [? leaning, ?] you see?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where there were some people who were more pro-Semitic, not anti-Semitic like in my area.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because my area was very, very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Kielce was a known place of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they beat her up, beat her up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Finally, the [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Spiegel ?] could not take the responsibility.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He asked her, Natka, what would happen?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
